{"tid":1473183,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"與一名父親對話後有感","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T09:20:19.000Z","uid":187235,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c8becc1398fe334a9c2222ed4eb2c484f168d1","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:46:32.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說頭先我喺深水埗等巴士<br />\n喺巴士站見到一對夫婦<br />\n男嘅就MMKK咁嘅金毛叔叔 <br />\n女嘅就似賢妻look 但係目光呆滯咁<br />\n <br />\n無意中聽到佢哋對話內容 就話等車等好耐 不如撘的士<br />\n我就用狗巴App睇下啦 之後就好心同佢講 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:就快有車㗎啦 因為前面有示威 所以可能會慢少少<br />\n<br />\n點知 個女人就攞串佛珠出嚟 一臉驚慌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢老公就同我講 8月5號當晚嘅事<br />\n<br />\n嗰日 佢喺荃灣食完飯 喺示威現場行過 <br />\n好心咁勸籲大家返屋企 但係因為佢當時著緊白衫<br />\n(但唔係真。白衫<br />\n發生咗一啲推撞 <br />\n而示威者喺電光火石間 又分辨唔到佢嘅身分 <br />\n大家一湧而上就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為咁 佢就入廠瞓咗幾日 身上仲有未癒嘅傷痕<br />\n<br />\n佢依家一家三口 仲有個喺老婆個肚入面 <br />\n如果因為咁而受重傷 真係會手停口停<br />\n因為咁樣 佢哋兩個先會對示威行動有咁大反應<br />\n呢個時候 我內疚到唔知點回應佢好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只能夠代當時嘅手足向佢哋道歉<br />\n<br />\n佢哋上咗巴士之後 事情就告一段落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcb6b7b922a49042b8064621ad957afd56029ef","tid":1473183,"uid":284565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借推一下，大學生請入<br />\n<br />\n［第三次po 了］做問卷籌錢俾612 人道支援基金<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430200</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2c45d269b5231a48938bc07195a8580c384e1377","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:01:01.000Z","msg":"我想講嘅係 <br />\n各位手足都係想保護大家 先會向白衫反擊<br />\n但係 我哋唔應該將怒意發洩喺錯嘅目標<br />\n何況當時嘅受害者連刀都冇把<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以用較低的武力 控制嫌疑者？(索帶/綁欄杆）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們不是暴徒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然如果有證據 點錫佢春袋都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點都唔割</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8.18民陣大遊行見</span>"},{"pid":"f4bd87c2b17ab0a3be3280ae7a0f1359fec36905","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:04:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f091a35d69a3eb70ba36cd2b3df7c3913dd27f9d","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:04:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"685036a7c0c9b1f1444cc65e7bc5cfcaf51ce21a","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:04:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e165a43ccacda60f387cf5a4015c3672af6cf8ca","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:04:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14344d90fd1f08989e9015f0bc808b4b4462d074","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:05:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"376484c85bf51a8f99263b1019c4e63f2ccc6333","tid":1473183,"uid":272243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"7db6e1e438a07772c32e784455ab8299a8594675","tid":1473183,"uid":187235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"咩事 點解咁多負評"},{"pid":"53d